  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving the resilience and living conditions of people affected by the conflict in eastern Ukraine through material and psycho-social support</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Zlep&#x161;enie odolnosti a&#x202F;&#x17E;ivotn&#xFD;ch podmienok &#x13E;ud&#xED; zasiahnut&#xFD;ch konfliktom na v&#xFD;chode Ukrajiny prostredn&#xED;ctvom materi&#xE1;lnej a&#x202F;psychosoci&#xE1;lnej podpory</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Projekt m&#xE1; za cie&#x13E; rie&#x161;i&#x165; probl&#xE9;my &#x13E;ud&#xED; &#x17E;ij&#xFA;cich na v&#xFD;chode Ukrajiny v Bakhmutskom a Avdiivskom regi&#xF3;ne v oblasti Donecku. Projekt zabezpe&#x10D;&#xED; rekon&#x161;trukciu 5 a vybavenie 15 soci&#xE1;lnych centier zameran&#xFD;ch na podporu det&#xED; a obyvate&#x13E;om regi&#xF3;nu bude poskytnut&#xE1; pomoc pri rie&#x161;en&#xED; ich psychosoci&#xE1;lnych probl&#xE9;mov, napr&#xED;klad s&#x202F;pracovn&#xFD;m a rodinn&#xFD;m &#x17E;ivotom. Podpor&#xED; sa t&#xFD;m odstra&#x148;ovanie n&#xE1;sledkov dlhodob&#xE9;ho ozbrojen&#xE9;ho konfliktu a t&#xFD;m prispeje k vytvoreniu lep&#x161;&#xED;ch predpokladov na soci&#xE1;lno-ekonomick&#xFD; rozvoj Ukrajiny.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to solve the problems of people living in the east of Ukraine in the Bakhmut and Avdiiv regions in the Donetsk area. The project will ensure the reconstruction of 5 and the equipment of 15 social centers aimed at supporting children and the inhabitants of the region will be provided with assistance in solving their psychosocial problems, for example, working and family life. This will support the elimination of the consequences of the long-term armed conflict and thus contribute to creating better conditions for the socio-economic development of Ukraine.</narrative>
  </description>
